1. Yes

2. Yes, you take either CS 370 or CS 375

3. Yes, you get ~$1800 remission as an 8 hour and ~$6500 remission as a 20 hour, in addition to your salary. Being an International student has no bearing on the remission amount.

That being said hiring is well underway so I'm not sure how many positions are even available at this point. You should probably apply ASAP
